track.name: Blunderbuss
comments: There’s a line at the very end of this song that could be one of the best lines I’ve heard in a long time. "Doin' what you people need is never on the menu." <3

Queens Of The Stone Age is borderline grunge rock - Jack White is not. I vote with the "they sound nothing like QOTSA" party. Oh, well I guess there is a guy singing lead vocals for both ... well, then maybe they do :-)
